794
01:17:31.700 --> 01:17:34.360
Yeah, his temper,
all the drinking…

795
01:17:34.400 --> 01:17:36.360
Well, Mom, you know.

796
01:17:36.400 --> 01:17:39.260
Everybody let's just remain calm.

797
01:17:39.300 --> 01:17:42.860
