833
01:21:15.300 --> 01:21:18.660
To help me keep it together
for them right now.

834
01:21:18.700 --> 01:21:21.892
Okay.

835
01:21:27.100 --> 01:21:29.700
How do you do this
with so many people?

836
01:21:30.600 --> 01:21:33.806
Strangers.

837
